A Virginia math teacher is facing a maximum of 22 years in prison for having sex with four of her students.

Erica Mesa, 28, pleaded guilty on Friday to two counts of electronic solicitation of a minor and two counts of contributing to the delinquency of a minor.

Mesa taught math at Colonial Forge High School. She pleaded guilty to charges involving two students but admitted having sex with two others aged 16 to 18.

