Defense attorney Mark Gardner said Mesa is not a pedophile and ‘was not preying on people who had no interest in participating.’

He had asked Judge Victoria Willis to release Mesa on bond until her sentencing, but the request was denied. 

Judge Willis said Mesa would have to 'clean up the mess you have made.'

Her guilty pleas means she will have to register as a sex offender.  

